---
title: Fragrant Chicken Stir-fry with green beans and coriander
description: Fresh chilli and gingery lemongrass paste make this a fragrant and exciting dish. This stir fry is inspired by a dish that in Thailand is known as  'Pad Krapow Moo'.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R11_W24_IE_IECC24150-3_Main_high-dc341544.jpg
